description: This file is a non-Sizzle jQuery selector module that provides custom selector functionalities with limited features, focusing on core DOM element selection and utility functions.

methods.name: find
methods.description: Finds elements matching a selector within a context, with optional seed elements.

methods.name: unique
methods.description: Removes duplicate elements from a results array.

methods.name: text
methods.description: Retrieves the text content of an element or array of elements.

methods.name: contains
methods.description: Checks if element a contains element b.

methods.name: isXMLDoc
methods.description: Determines if a document is an XML document.
